\c 6
\s Erisha anopapamadza sanhu pamusoro pemvura
\p
\v 1 Zvino vanakomana vevaporofita vakati kuna Erisha\x + 2.3.\x*: Tarirai ikozvino, nzvimbo patigere mberi kwako yakamanikana zvikuru kwatiri.
\v 2 Regai henyu tiende kuJoridhani tigonotora kubvako umwe neumwe danda, uye ngatizviitirei nzvimboko \add ye\add*kugarako. Iye ndokuti: Endai.
\v 3 Zvino umwe wakati: Tendai henyu mugoenda nevaranda venyu. Iye ndokuti: Ini ndichaenda.
\v 4 Zvino wakaenda navo. Pavakasvika kuJoridhani, vakatema matanda.
\v 5 Asi umwe wakati achitema danda, musoro wedemo ndokuwira mumvura. Zvino wakadanidzira ndokuti: Haiwa, tenzi wangu! Nokuti raiva rakweretwa\x + 4.3.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino munhu waMwari wakati: Rawira papi? Iye ndokumuratidza nzvimbo. Zvino wakatema rutanda ndokurukandapo ndokupapamadza demo\x + 2.21.\x*.
\v 7 Zvino wakati: Zvisimudzire. Iye ndokutandavadza ruoko rwake ndokuritora.
\s VaSiriya vanopofumadzwa paSamariya
\p
\v 8 Zvino mambo weSiriya wairwisana naIsraeri; ndokurangana nevaranda vake achiti: Panzvimbo yekuti neyekuti uchava musasa wangu.
\v 9 Zvino munhu waMwari wakatuma kuna mambo waIsraeri achiti: Chenjera usapfuurira kunzvimbo iyi, nokuti VaSiriya voburukirapo\x + 1 Madz. 20.7.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino mambo waIsraeri wakatuma kunzvimbo iyo munhu waMwari yaaiva ataura kwaari nekumuyambira nezvayo, ndokuchengetedzekako, kwete kamwe uye kwete kaviri\x + Eki. 18.20.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino moyo wamambo weSiriya wakagumbuka nekuda kwechinhu ichi; iye ndokudana varanda vake ndokuti kwavari: Hamungandiudzi here kuti ndiani patiri ari wamambo waIsraeri?
\v 12 Zvino umwe wevaranda vake wakati: Kwete, ishe wangu mambo, asi Erisha muporofita ari muIsraeri anoudza mambo waIsraeri mashoko amunotaura muimba yenyu yekurara.
\v 13 Iye ndokuti: Endai muone paari kuti nditume ndimutore. Zvino wakaudzwa zvikanzi: Tarirai, ari paDhotani\x + Gen.. 37.17.\x*.
\v 14 Zvino wakatumako mabhiza nengoro nehondo huru; zvino vakasvika usiku, ndokukomba guta.
\p
\v 15 Muranda wemunhu waMwari paakamuka mangwanani-ngwanani, wakabuda, zvino tarira, hondo yakakomba guta pamwe nemabhiza nengoro. Muranda wake ndokuti kwaari: Haiwa, tenzi wangu! Tichaita sei?
\v 16 Zvino iye wakati: Usatya, nokuti vanesu vakawanda kupfuura vaanavo\x + 2 Makor. 32.7. Map. 55.18.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino Erisha wakanyengetera ndokuti: Jehovha, zarurai henyu meso ake kuti aone. Jehovha ndokuzarura meso ejaya iro, iro ndokuona, zvino tarira, gomo rizere nemabhiza nengoro dzemoto zvakakomba Erisha\x + 2.11. Map. 34.7. Zek. 1.8. 6.1-7.\x*.
\v 18 Pavakaburukira kwaari, Erisha wakanyengetera kuna Jehovha, ndokuti: Rovai henyu rudzi urwu neupofu\x + Gen.. 19.11.\x*. Zvino wakavarova neupofu zvichienderana neshoko raErisha.
\v 19 Erisha ndokuti kwavari: Haisi iyo nzira, uye harisi iro guta; nditeverei, ndichakuisai kumunhu uyu wamunotsvaka. Zvino wakavaisa kuSamariya.
\p
\v 20 Zvino zvakaitika pakupinda kwavo muSamariya kuti Erisha wakati: Jehovha, zarurai meso evava kuti vaone. Jehovha ndokuzarura meso avo, zvino ndokuona, zvino tarira, vaiva pakati peSamariya\x + 6.17.\x*.
\v 21 Mambo waIsraeri wakati achivaona ndokuti kuna Erisha: Baba vangu, ndirove here, ndirove here\x + 8.9. 5.13.\x*?
\v 22 Iye ndokuti: Usarova. Ungarova here avo vawatapa nemunondo wako kana neuta hwako\x + Gen.. 48.22.\x*? Isa chingwa nemvura pamberi pavo kuti vadye vanwe vagoenda kuna tenzi wavo\x + VaRom. 12.20.\x*.
\v 23 Zvino iye wakavagadzirira mabiko makuru; vakati vadya nekunwa, wakavaendesa, ivo ndokuenda kuna tenzi wavo. Naizvozvo hondo dzakarongwa dzeSiriya hadzina kuzopamha kudzoka kunyika yaIsraeri\x + 6.8,9. 5.2. 13.20. 24.2. 2 Makor. 22.1. 25.9,10,13. 26.11.\x*.
\s Bheni-Hadhadhi anokomba Samariya, asi anokundwa
\p
\v 24 Zvino zvakaitika shure kweizvi kuti Bheni-Hadhadhi mambo weSiriya wakaunganidza hondo yake yose ndokukwira ndokukomba Samariya\x + 1 Madz. 20.2.\x*.
\v 25 Nzara huru ndokuva paSamariya; zvino tarira, vaikomba kusvika musoro wembongoro wava wemasirivha makumi masere, nechechina chechiyero chematoto enjiva pamasirivha mashanu.
\v 26 Zvino zvakaitika mambo waIsraeri wakati achipfuura neparusvingo, kwakadanidzira mukadzi kwaari achiti: Batsirai, Ishe wangu, mambo!
\v 27 Iye ndokuti: Jehovha asingakubatsiri; ndingakubatsira nezvinobvepi? Zvinobva paburiro kana pachisviniro chewaini here\x + Num.. 18.27,30.\x*?
\v 28 Zvino mambo wakati kwaari: Unei? Iye ndokuti: Mukadzi uyu wakati kwandiri: Uya nemwanakomana wako kuti timudye nhasi, uye mangwana tichadya mwanakomana wangu.
\v 29 Zvino takabika mwanakomana wangu ndokumudya; zvino ndakati kwaari nezuva raitevera: Uya nemwanakomana wako kuti timudye. Asi iye wakavanza mwanakomana wake\x + Det. 28.53. Eze. 5.10.\x*.
\v 30 Zvino zvakaitika mambo paakanzwa mashoko emukadzi uyu kuti wakadambura nguvo dzake\x + 1 Madz. 21.27. Gen.. 44.13.\x*; zvino waipfuura neparusvingo; vanhu ndokuona, uye tarira, kwaiva nemasaga pamuviri wake mukati\x + 1 Madz. 21.27. Gen.. 44.13.\x*.
\v 31 Zvino wakati: Mwari ngaaite saizvozvo kwandiri uye saizvozvo awedzere, kana musoro waErisha mwanakomana waShafati ukagara paari nhasi\x + Rut. 1.17.\x*.
\v 32 Asi Erisha waiva agere muimba yake, uye vakuru vaiva vagere naye\x + Eze. 8.1. 14.1. 20.1.\x*; ndokutuma munhu mberi kwake; nhume isati yasvika kwaari, iyewo wakati kuvakuru: Munoona here kuti mwana uyu wemhondi watuma kuzobvisa musoro wangu\x + Isa. 1.21. 1 Madz. 18.4. 21.13.\x*? Tarirai, panosvika nhume mupfige mukova, muitsikirire pamukova; hausi mutsindo wetsoka dzatenzi wake here shure kwake\x + 7.17.\x*?
\v 33 Wakati achiri kutaura navo, zvino tarira, nhume yakaburukira kwaari; iye ndokuti: Tarirai, chakaipa ichi chinobva kuna Jehovha; ndichakamirirei Jehovha\x + Job. 2.9.\x*?
